text: Jannez is a dansband from Laxsjö, Sweden, established in 1976 as Stars orkester. In September 1996, the band scored a Svensktoppen hit for two weeks with the song De blindas café.Svensktoppen - 1996 Jannez participated at Dansbandskampen 2008, performing Paul Paljett's 1977 song Guenerina. == Discography == === Albums === *"Härliga tider - strålande tider! - 1989 *"Någonstans i mitt hjärta - 1994 *"Någonsdans i Sverige - 2001 *"Guenerina - 2009 *"Se på oss nu - 2010 *"É skiiv ma bäre gammaldans... - 2011 == Svensktoppen songs == *"De blindas café" - 1996 ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:Dansbands Category:Musical groups established in 1976
